{
  "texts": [
    "As shown in Fig. 1a, each trait node (if it has child trait nodes) can be left-clicked, triggering the appearance of a window containing a subgraph and a list that intuitively illustrates the child traits and related genes of the selected trait node.",
    "Due to space limitation, only trait data from the root to 4-level for each crop are plotted.",
    "Meanwhile, the query function via gene or phenotype is provided so that users can drill down to access complete detailed data.",
    "Gene browse page.",
    "We allow users to search and browse by gene name or gene symbol (Fig. 1a)."
  ]
}